Interface MappedSignalView<T>

All Superinterfaces:
SignalView<T>
public interface MappedSignalView<T>
extends SignalView<T>

An interface implemented by SignalViews that represent a mapping of some underlying model, and which necessarily require the use of a Connection under the hood. This interface allows the connection to be accessed so that it may be cleared if desired.

Method Summary

          Returns the connection that maintains this mapped signal.
